casebody.data:
Lorna CLAUSE, petitioner,
v.
UNITED STATES DISTRICT COURT FOR the EASTERN DISTRICT OF MISSOURI, et al. No. 16-641. Supreme Court of the United States Jan. 17, 2017.

Motion of The Pension Rights Center for leave to file a brief as amicus curiae granted. Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Eighth Circuit denied.
